# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_MODEL_MAX_TRACTION

## Summary
Get the maximum traction force this vehicles tyres can apply

## Parameters
* **MODEL_NAMES** vehicleModelHashKey: VehicleModelName - model name of vehicle

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Useful links
- [VHub: Vehicles](https://vhub.wiki/vehicles)

## Notes
Returns max traction of the specified vehicle model.
